English: Revives on death, fully restores character
Spanish (EU): Revive al morir, restaura al personaje

English:
Item for online duelist play. Enchanted by incantations of the Golden Order Fundamentalists. Used to bring back a duelist from the brink of death upon their defeat, and restore them to their natural state.
On death, fully heals HP, FP, restores poise, removes all ailments and dispels all special effects.
Spanish (EU): Objeto para duelos en multijugador en línea. Hechizado con encantaciones de Fundamentalistas del Orden Dorado. Se usa para rescatar a un duelista de las puertas de la muerte al ser derrotado, y restaurarles a su estado normal. Al morir, cura los PV, PC, el equilibrio, elimina toda aflicción y efecto especial.

English: Item for online duelist play. Enchanted by incantations of the Golden Order Fundamentalists. Used to quickly restore duelists to their natural state before a battle. Fully heals HP, FP, restores poise, removes all ailments and dispels all special effects.
Spanish (EU): Objeto para duelos en multijugador en línea. Hechizado con encantaciones de Fundamentalistas del Orden Dorado. Se usa para restaurar a un duelista a su estado normal antes de la batalla. Cura los PV, PC, el equilibrio, elimina toda aflicción y efecto especial.

English: Grants an infinite supply of any currently held good
Spanish (EU): Otorga un suministro ilimitado de cualquier bien actualmente sujetado

English: Item for online duelist play. Used to store and retain an infinite supply of goods. Any items used will retain their current quantity. A peculiar bottomless jar. Its origins are unknown. Some deride it as a symbol of unbridled avarice.
Spanish (EU): Objeto para duelos en multijugador en línea. Se usa para almacenar y retener un suministro infinito de bienes. Cualquier objeto usado mantendrá su cantidad actual. Un peculiar tarro sin fondo. Sus orígenes son desconocidos. Algunos lo ridiculizan como un símbolo de avaricia sin límites.

English: Calls phantoms who left their red sign to join your world
Spanish (EU): Calls phantoms who left their red sign to join your world

English: Item for online duelist play. Enchanted by incantations of the Golden Order Fundamentalists. Used to call phantoms who left their red sign to join your world. Requires for at least one phantom to be present in the world already.
Spanish (EU): Item for online duelist play. Enchanted by incantations of the Golden Order Fundamentalists. Used to call phantoms who left their red sign to join your world.
